Create EC2 instance DB client  to connect to the RDS instance 

Step 1 Create EC2 instance with ubuntu OS and connect to it

Step 2 Install mysql client in EC2 instance



sudo apt update
sudo apt upgrade
sudo apt install mysql-client
mysql --version


Step 3 Connect with endpoint  
mysql -h <endpoint>  -u admin -p 
